name: EVC Charge
body:
# EVC Charge
Simple, clean, elegant - a better way to charge.

##Features
* simple, fluid user experience
* quick, no-frills search
* detailed pushpins with descriptions of each station
* compatible with both touchscreen and desktop configurations

###Created by nahTeCh
Made by a student - for you!
